data.description: Beautiful spacious 2 bedroom/2 bath/1 Car Garage Townhouse nestled in maintained Eagle Palms!   This GATED COMMUNITY is actively monitored and managed access. COMMUNITY POOL, ponds, mature landscaping, palm trees and lighted sidewalks. Open floor plan and vaulted ceilings! NEW ROOF, NEW LAMINATE FLOORING and fresh paint.   The staircase boasts soaring ceilings leading to the second floor with an open feel, DUAL Primary En-Suites. The hall closet houses the stackable laundry with washer/dryer that convey. Ceiling fans throughout. The clubhouse, community mailboxes, and pool are a short walk away. Low HOA fees includes exterior paint, general landscaping, exterior pest control, garbage removal and water.  Just a short distance to our amazing Florida beaches, Tampa, airport, theme parks and shopping. Easy commute access to I4, I75, & The Crosstown Expressway.
